# argo graphify — commit ONLY the 3 durable artifacts; ignore everything else in
# graphify-out (bulk viz, caches, manifests, metadata). graph.json carries the
# embedded community labels Claude reads. Globs cover monorepo (per-workspace
# graphify-out/) and single-app (root graphify-out/) alike.
# setup-claude appends this to the project's .gitignore.
**/graphify-out/*
!**/graphify-out/graph.json
!**/graphify-out/GRAPH_REPORT.md
!**/graphify-out/.graphify_labels.json
